 is number of inputs and 
\begin_inset Formula $n_{j+1}$
\end_inset

 is number of ouptuts:
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
W\sim U\left[-\frac{\sqrt{6}}{\sqrt{n_{j}+n_{j+1}}},-\frac{\sqrt{6}}{\sqrt{n_{j}+n_{j+1}}}\right]
